title: MMX
subtitle: Martian Moons eXploration
paragraphs: A Japanese (JAXA) mission to travel to Mars and survey the Red Planet's two moons, Phobos and Deimos. The spacecraft will explore both moons and collect a sample of Phobos and bring it to Earth.

metadata_table.value: Clarify the origin of the two Martian moons and the evolution process of Mars, Phobos and Deimos
